body:
## Hi, I'm Kurtis

I'm a Mechanical Engineering student at [U.Va.](http://seas.virginia.edu)

I develop software for the (Center for Open Science)[http://cos.io]

You can see what I build for work (and for play) on (Github)[https://github.com/kmjungersen].

I also drive busses for U.Va.'s bus service, (The University Transit Service)[http://www.virginia.edu/parking/uts/]

If you want to get in touch, (shoot me an email!)[mailto:Kurtis@kmjungersen.com]
